{"tid":1286492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個再提武漢就係鬼","createTime":"2019-07-05T01:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T13:30:09.000Z","uid":76310,"like":92,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6640c7f7b3bcb3ba3310ede7c2bf199b7b0c63e1","tid":1286492,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"如果係5毛提出都算<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑真係成班真心 覺得要支持武漢<br />\n仲話武漢起義<br />\n<br />\n呢種思維正正就是當年愛国不愛黨既思維的精髓<br />\n<br />\n今次武漢單野個性質係維權<br />\n維權既意思係保障自己利益不要受損<br />\n中国人既思維沒有公平 沒有公義 沒有開放 沒有民主 沒有平等概念 佢地只有利益。<br />\n中国人不是不滿意獨裁甚至帝制，他們只不過不滿意自己不是制度下的受益者，公平公義與否不重要，最重要是自己受益<br />\n<br />\n武漢既人都話中共是好的 是先進的 是文明的<br />\n現在遊行示威只不過是維權<br />\n和追求公平公義平等民主 0關係<br />\n<br />\n而且不要再落入當日的陷阱，覺得中国人是好的，衰的只係中共<br />\n周街柯 鑽漏洞搵著數 毒疫苗 毒奶粉 造假 抄襲 無道德 大家日日見 你覺得自己要和中国人拉上關係 無人阻到你<br />\n<br />\n如果你硬要提武漢 你等同承認自己是愛国的中国人一樣"},{"pid":"7c7702bcb49f88f0e48c3099cefe8fe47d216b10","tid":1286492,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"所以大家明白點解當日回歸民主中国<br />\n今日班強国人做咁多衰野 都成班傻閪仲咁愛佢地 愛国不愛黨 中国人是美好的<br />\n<br />\n何況當日呢"},{"pid":"04968ca654f769f0d81cfa7c8a59b3348c8effb4","tid":1286492,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"成班大中華上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747baae5e205c3517f13a5878efaaea01efaccea","tid":1286492,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bde30c3ca6da357b074dc8e51ba283135a55a2","tid":1286492,"uid":403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"武漢=鄰國的事"},{"pid":"0d01822d515110d4a5e16529a6d2f6ff8ec476f2","tid":1286492,"uid":106856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n人有人做,我地自己顧好自己先"},{"pid":"5f86f6a473c1f759bc41c3b348cfd5fdaf857904","tid":1286492,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:52:54.000Z","msg":"武漢人：港獨分子唔好諗住利用我地<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好自作多情<br />\n<br />\n要撐就撐分離主義滬獨川獨疆獨圖獨台獨<br />\n<br />\n集中五大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"097becfe5522fa9931439c03f476d14dd60085b6","tid":1286492,"uid":30384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"大中華膠正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1f939d47796669588c3df602eb33ed27f273d0","tid":1286492,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:04:35.000Z","msg":"佢地根本就係not in my backyard. 唔係真心反對惡政，而係嗱，你咪起喺我後面，你搬遠100公里，睇佢地行唔行出來啦。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc96c96bd68f9bc12db5e20f6db760668bb8bf1","tid":1286492,"uid":213018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"我啱啱提咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a70066228e2a2f1a77c721f63464286ec72b0d7","tid":1286492,"uid":119055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n俾更多人見到"},{"pid":"760321fa4513ca1cb09c4f5557a9dfd9416c805a","tid":1286492,"uid":244310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:10:01.000Z","msg":"不如唔出聲Del app 就唔係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77a4b06f4a1e0649014231dcc778314dd6bcac5","tid":1286492,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"唔好捉鬼，200萬人裡面一定有人係真心大中華<br />\n佢地想搞咪搞，兄弟爬山<br />\n不過唔好騎劫個遊行"},{"pid":"43e5ade6d7923afa126c0165a56ef590695c30dc","tid":1286492,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:11:00.000Z","msg":"推，佢地個本質跟本唔一樣，你話唔係既，佢地遊行係要民主，咁緊係拉埋佢地，而家佢地只喺維權，同我哋完全唔同。"},{"pid":"27a168f33aa29c5b05af93fbd7323c8c848388bd","tid":1286492,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7887fc767b55fb0b63ce4f464b0f115ff5dc1019","tid":1286492,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"2919149c5ae4119f93e48a357017d68a7178c99e","tid":1286492,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1f939d47796669588c3df602eb33ed27f273d0","tid":1286492,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:04:35.000Z","msg":"佢地根本就係not in my backyard. 唔係真心反對惡政，而係嗱，你咪起喺我後面，你搬遠100公里，睇佢地行唔行出來啦。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"正是<br />\n<br />\n搬遠d 其他人仆街就無問題<br />\n我仆街就要出黎維權"},{"pid":"9d4ee263db6c54642e5812d687d6a478bc9d50d5","tid":1286492,"uid":263176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"NONONONONO <br />\n<br />\n提武昌係因為香港而家都係under 中國. <br />\n<br />\n有料入中國, 就會令到外國更明白香港逼似性. <br />\n好多外國野好怕香港會變64. <br />\n而武昌單野,正正話比全世界知有可能. <br />\n而香港要安全, 必須要國際庇護"},{"pid":"481c99ee47a01e7c4c204825b0fd0f98832b13cd","tid":1286492,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5835d05ad0dac79fb5cdb2ea4d9144d12bdd29dd","tid":1286492,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人整文宣叫果日遊行唔好提武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.